# Security response headers, served by Cloudflare Workers Static Assets (it honors _headers).
# Addresses the (unscored) Lighthouse security recommendations: a Content Security Policy,
# a strong HSTS policy (with preload), and clickjacking / MIME protections.
#
# CSP notes for maintainers:
#   - script-src is tight: 'self' + the inline anti-FOUC theme script ('unsafe-inline',
#     unavoidable on a static build with no per-request nonce) + the Cloudflare Web
#     Analytics beacon. It still blocks externally-loaded scripts.
#   - img-src / media-src allow https: so Sanity images (cdn.sanity.io) and editor-added
#     images / background videos load.
#   - frame-src lists the embeds actually used (YouTube, Vimeo, Google Maps). If a church
#     later adds a Subsplash / Planning Center script or iframe embed via the page builder,
#     add its origin to script-src / frame-src.
#   - connect-src covers the contact forms (Web3Forms) + analytics; add a newsletter or
#     Formspree origin here if one is enabled.
#   - hCaptcha (form anti-spam) needs https://hcaptcha.com + https://*.hcaptcha.com in
#     script-src (api.js pulls helpers from newassets.hcaptcha.com), frame-src (the
#     challenge iframe), connect-src (its API), and style-src. Without these the widget
#     is silently blocked and never appears. NOTE: a plain local static preview does NOT
#     send these headers, so always sanity-check captcha rendering against `wrangler dev`
#     (npm run preview) or the live site, not just a static file server.
#   - frame-ancestors is 'self' (the Studio iframe "Preview" was removed, so the live site
#     no longer needs to be embedded by the Studio).
#   - Trusted Types is intentionally NOT enabled: require-trusted-types-for would break the
#     YouTube / Vimeo / Maps / analytics / embed scripts.

/*
  Strict-Transport-Security: max-age=63072000; includeSubDomains; preload
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  Cross-Origin-Opener-Policy: same-origin
  Content-Security-Policy: default-src 'self'; base-uri 'self'; object-src 'none'; frame-ancestors 'self'; img-src 'self' data: https:; media-src 'self' https:; font-src 'self'; style-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://hcaptcha.com https://*.hcaptcha.com; script-src 'self' 'unsafe-inline' https://static.cloudflareinsights.com https://hcaptcha.com https://*.hcaptcha.com; connect-src 'self' https://api.web3forms.com https://cloudflareinsights.com https://hcaptcha.com https://*.hcaptcha.com; frame-src 'self' https://www.youtube.com https://www.youtube-nocookie.com https://player.vimeo.com https://www.google.com https://maps.google.com https://hcaptcha.com https://*.hcaptcha.com; form-action 'self' https://api.web3forms.com; upgrade-insecure-requests
